" time.", "tokens": [50879, 565, 13, 50933], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17143202416690778, "compression_ratio": 1.4852941176470589, "no_speech_prob": 2.8495012339285752e-12}, {"id": 42, "seek": 15484, "start": 166.2, "end": 171.08, "text": " This is known as an O-1 process, meaning the algorithm takes the exact same amount of time", "tokens": [50933, 639, 307, 2570, 382, 364, 422, 12, 16, 1399, 11, 3620, 264, 9284, 2516, 264, 1900, 912, 2372, 295, 565, 51177], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17143202416690778, "compression_ratio": 1.4852941176470589, "no_speech_prob": 2.8495012339285752e-12}, {"id": 43, "seek": 15484, "start": 171.08, "end": 173.62, "text": " to run, regardless of how much data you feed it.", "tokens": [51177, 281, 1190, 11, 10060, 295, 577, 709, 1412, 291, 3154, 309, 13, 51304], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17143202416690778, "compression_ratio": 1.4852941176470589, "no_speech_prob": 2.8495012339285752e-12}, {"id": 44, "seek": 17362, "start": 173.62, "end": 180.4, "text": " By analyzing the spacing of these jitter patterns, the system immediately drops high-entropy background", "tokens": [50365, 3146, 23663, 264, 27739, 295, 613, 361, 3904, 8294, 11, 264, 1185, 4258, 11438, 1090, 12, 317, 27514, 3678, 50704], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 45, "seek": 17362, "start": 180.4, "end": 181.4, "text": " noise.", "tokens": [50704, 5658, 13, 50754], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 46, "seek": 17362, "start": 181.4, "end": 186.62, "text": " It only passes through the signals that contain clear structural meaning or emotional intent.", "tokens": [50754, 467, 787, 11335, 807, 264, 12354, 300, 5304, 1850, 15067, 3620, 420, 6863, 8446, 13, 51015], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 47, "seek": 17362, "start": 186.62, "end": 191.82, "text": " Dropping the noise at the very perimeter ensures the system doesn't drown in data exhaust.", "tokens": [51015, 35305, 3759, 264, 5658, 412, 264, 588, 32404, 28111, 264, 1185, 1177, 380, 20337, 294, 1412, 14687, 13, 51275], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 48, "seek": 17362, "start": 191.82, "end": 197.26, "text": " It gives the AI the capacity to focus its attention on a specific event, rather than processing", "tokens": [51275, 467, 2709, 264, 7318, 264, 6042, 281, 1879, 1080, 3202, 322, 257, 2685, 2280, 11, 2831, 813, 9007, 51547], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 49, "seek": 17362, "start": 197.26, "end": 199.0, "text": " everything equally.", "tokens": [51547, 1203, 12309, 13, 51634], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102831872661462, "compression_ratio": 1.644, "no_speech_prob": 3.409513773741657e-12}, {"id": 50, "seek": 19900, "start": 199.0, "end": 201.18, "text": " The clock hits 0.3 seconds.", "tokens": [50365, 440, 7830, 8664, 1958, 13, 18, 3949, 13, 50474], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 51, "seek": 19900, "start": 201.18, "end": 206.22, "text": " The filtered, meaningful signal now moves into the system's cerebral cortex, an environment", "tokens": [50474, 440, 37111, 11, 10995, 6358, 586, 6067, 666, 264, 1185, 311, 43561, 33312, 11, 364, 2823, 50726], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 52, "seek": 19900, "start": 206.22, "end": 209.52, "text": " the developers call the MEM-8 wave grid.", "tokens": [50726, 264, 8849, 818, 264, 40524, 12, 23, 5772, 10748, 13, 50891], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 53, "seek": 19900, "start": 209.52, "end": 212.76, "text": " Here we see the departure from traditional database storage.", "tokens": [50891, 1692, 321, 536, 264, 25866, 490, 5164, 8149, 6725, 13, 51053], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 54, "seek": 19900, "start": 212.76, "end": 216.82, "text": " The incoming data is not saved as a text file or a single coordinate.", "tokens": [51053, 440, 22341, 1412, 307, 406, 6624, 382, 257, 2487, 3991, 420, 257, 2167, 15670, 13, 51256], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 55, "seek": 19900, "start": 216.82, "end": 220.24, "text": " It blossoms into a physical, three-dimensional wave.", "tokens": [51256, 467, 47789, 666, 257, 4001, 11, 1045, 12, 18759, 5772, 13, 51427], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 56, "seek": 19900, "start": 220.24, "end": 224.12, "text": " The physical structure of this wave carries specific information.", "tokens": [51427, 440, 4001, 3877, 295, 341, 5772, 16402, 2685, 1589, 13, 51621], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08985563119252522, "compression_ratio": 1.55893536121673, "no_speech_prob": 2.6454370378320435e-12}, {"id": 57, "seek": 22412, "start": 224.12, "end": 230.94, "text": " The frequency, the distance between the peaks, encodes the semantic meaning of the concept itself.", "tokens": [50365, 440, 7893, 11, 264, 4560, 1296, 264, 26897, 11, 2058, 4789, 264, 47982, 3620, 295, 264, 3410, 2564, 13, 50706], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 58, "seek": 22412, "start": 230.94, "end": 235.66, "text": " The amplitude, or the overall height of the wave, is modulated by the emotional weight", "tokens": [50706, 440, 27433, 11, 420, 264, 4787, 6681, 295, 264, 5772, 11, 307, 1072, 6987, 538, 264, 6863, 3364, 50942], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 59, "seek": 22412, "start": 235.66, "end": 237.0, "text": " of the event.", "tokens": [50942, 295, 264, 2280, 13, 51009], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 60, "seek": 22412, "start": 237.0, "end": 243.26, "text": " And the phase, where the wave begins its cycle, locks in the exact temporal relationship.", "tokens": [51009, 400, 264, 5574, 11, 689, 264, 5772, 7338, 1080, 6586, 11, 20703, 294, 264, 1900, 30881, 2480, 13, 51322], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 61, "seek": 22412, "start": 243.26, "end": 248.0, "text": " When it's time to recall a memory, the system doesn't execute a search query.", "tokens": [51322, 1133, 309, 311, 565, 281, 9901, 257, 4675, 11, 264, 1185, 1177, 380, 14483, 257, 3164, 14581, 13, 51559], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 62, "seek": 22412, "start": 248.0, "end": 250.76, "text": " It drops a new probe wave into the grid.", "tokens": [51559, 467, 11438, 257, 777, 22715, 5772, 666, 264, 10748, 13, 51697], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06239737614546672, "compression_ratio": 1.6126482213438735, "no_speech_prob": 2.794145990969721e-12}, {"id": 63, "seek": 25076, "start": 250.76, "end": 255.7, "text": " If that probe encounters stored memory waves with similar frequencies, they physically amplify", "tokens": [50365, 759, 300, 22715, 26310, 12187, 4675, 9417, 365, 2531, 20250, 11, 436, 9762, 41174, 50612], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07386144399642944, "compression_ratio": 1.5731707317073171, "no_speech_prob": 2.4183446044323542e-12}, {"id": 64, "seek": 25076, "start": 255.7, "end": 258.52, "text": " one another through constructive interference.", "tokens": [50612, 472, 1071, 807, 30223, 24497, 13, 50753], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07386144399642944, "compression_ratio": 1.5731707317073171, "no_speech_prob": 2.4183446044323542e-12}, {"id": 65, "seek": 25076, "start": 258.52, "end": 263.62, "text": " Retrieving information becomes a physical reaction, rather than a mathematical lookup.", "tokens": [50753, 11495, 5469, 798, 1589, 3643, 257, 4001, 5480, 11, 2831, 813, 257, 18894, 574, 1010, 13, 51008], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07386144399642944, "compression_ratio": 1.5731707317073171, "no_speech_prob": 2.4183446044323542e-12}, {"id": 66, "seek": 25076, "start": 263.62, "end": 269.48, "text": " The correct memories naturally ring out, bypassing the bottlenecks of scanning millions of records.", "tokens": [51008, 440, 3006, 8495, 8195, 4875, 484, 11, 24996, 278, 264, 44641, 2761, 295, 27019, 6803, 295, 7724, 13, 51301], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07386144399642944, "compression_ratio": 1.5731707317073171, "no_speech_prob": 2.4183446044323542e-12}, {"id": 67, "seek": 25076, "start": 269.48, "end": 274.03999999999996, "text": " At the 1.02 mark, the software hits a hardware constraint.", "tokens": [51301, 1711, 264, 502, 13, 12756, 1491, 11, 264, 4722, 8664, 257, 8837, 25534, 13, 51529], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07386144399642944, "compression_ratio": 1.5731707317073171, "no_speech_prob": 2.4183446044323542e-12}, {"id": 68, "seek": 27404, "start": 274.04, "end": 279.86, "text": " This complex 3D wave interference pattern has to be saved onto the flat, two-dimensional architecture", "tokens": [50365, 639, 3997, 805, 35, 5772, 24497, 5102, 575, 281, 312, 6624, 3911, 264, 4962, 11, 732, 12, 18759, 9482, 50656], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 69, "seek": 27404, "start": 279.86, "end": 281.72, "text": " of a solid-state drive.", "tokens": [50656, 295, 257, 5100, 12, 15406, 3332, 13, 50749], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 70, "seek": 27404, "start": 281.72, "end": 284.62, "text": " The developers solve this using a Hilbert curve.", "tokens": [50749, 440, 8849, 5039, 341, 1228, 257, 19914, 4290, 7605, 13, 50894], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 71, "seek": 27404, "start": 284.62, "end": 289.54, "text": " This is a continuous, fractal space-filling curve that can fold a three-dimensional volume", "tokens": [50894, 639, 307, 257, 10957, 11, 17948, 304, 1901, 12, 69, 7345, 7605, 300, 393, 4860, 257, 1045, 12, 18759, 5523, 51140], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 72, "seek": 27404, "start": 289.54, "end": 292.24, "text": " into a single, one-dimensional line.", "tokens": [51140, 666, 257, 2167, 11, 472, 12, 18759, 1622, 13, 51275], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 73, "seek": 27404, "start": 292.24, "end": 297.28000000000003, "text": " It flattens out the data to write it sequentially to the disk, while perfectly preserving the spatial", "tokens": [51275, 467, 932, 1591, 694, 484, 264, 1412, 281, 2464, 309, 5123, 3137, 281, 264, 12355, 11, 1339, 6239, 33173, 264, 23598, 51527], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 74, "seek": 27404, "start": 297.28000000000003, "end": 300.16, "text": " proximity of the original memory waves.", "tokens": [51527, 27632, 295, 264, 3380, 4675, 9417, 13, 51671], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08364339706000931, "compression_ratio": 1.6323529411764706, "no_speech_prob": 2.883070952114375e-12}, {"id": 75, "seek": 30016, "start": 300.16, "end": 303.42, "text": " The timer crosses the 1.37-second mark.", "tokens": [50365, 440, 19247, 28467, 264, 502, 13, 12851, 12, 27375, 1491, 13, 50528], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 76, "seek": 30016, "start": 303.42, "end": 307.58000000000004, "text": " The immediate conscious loop is complete, but the system's work is not over.", "tokens": [50528, 440, 11629, 6648, 6367, 307, 3566, 11, 457, 264, 1185, 311, 589, 307, 406, 670, 13, 50736], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 77, "seek": 30016, "start": 307.58000000000004, "end": 311.74, "text": " A background protocol called the custodian takes over when the AI is idle.", "tokens": [50736, 316, 3678, 10336, 1219, 264, 14884, 378, 952, 2516, 670, 562, 264, 7318, 307, 30650, 13, 50944], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 78, "seek": 30016, "start": 311.74, "end": 317.02000000000004, "text": " It forces the operating system into mandatory sleep cycles, mimicking biological non-REM and", "tokens": [50944, 467, 5874, 264, 7447, 1185, 666, 22173, 2817, 17796, 11, 12247, 10401, 13910, 2107, 12, 3850, 44, 293, 51208], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 79, "seek": 30016, "start": 317.02000000000004, "end": 322.40000000000003, "text": " REM sleep, to replay and consolidate strong wave patterns, and delete the weak ones.", "tokens": [51208, 45991, 2817, 11, 281, 23836, 293, 49521, 2068, 5772, 8294, 11, 293, 12097, 264, 5336, 2306, 13, 51477], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 80, "seek": 30016, "start": 322.40000000000003, "end": 327.24, "text": " Tying the data to strict hardware locations and forcing the system offline for maintenance keeps", "tokens": [51477, 314, 1840, 264, 1412, 281, 10910, 8837, 9253, 293, 19030, 264, 1185, 21857, 337, 11258, 5965, 51719], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1190600041989927, "compression_ratio": 1.5904436860068258, "no_speech_prob": 3.0570262033596807e-12}, {"id": 81, "seek": 32724, "start": 327.24, "end": 329.5, "text": " the memory from fracturing over time.", "tokens": [50365, 264, 4675, 490, 17948, 1345, 670, 565, 13, 50478], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 82, "seek": 32724, "start": 329.5, "end": 333.84000000000003, "text": " It is a biological solution to the catastrophic memory fragmentation that plagues continuous", "tokens": [50478, 467, 307, 257, 13910, 3827, 281, 264, 34915, 4675, 9241, 19631, 300, 499, 7063, 10957, 50695], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 83, "seek": 32724, "start": 333.84000000000003, "end": 335.42, "text": " learning models.", "tokens": [50695, 2539, 5245, 13, 50774], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 84, "seek": 32724, "start": 335.42, "end": 338.68, "text": " Building the system this way tackles the symbol grounding problem.", "tokens": [50774, 18974, 264, 1185, 341, 636, 9426, 904, 264, 5986, 46727, 1154, 13, 50937], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 85, "seek": 32724, "start": 338.68, "end": 344.96000000000004, "text": " This is a challenge in computer science, where an AI manipulates symbols without ever understanding", "tokens": [50937, 639, 307, 257, 3430, 294, 3820, 3497, 11, 689, 364, 7318, 9258, 26192, 16944, 1553, 1562, 3701, 51251], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 86, "seek": 32724, "start": 344.96000000000004, "end": 347.96000000000004, "text": " what they represent in the physical world.", "tokens": [51251, 437, 436, 2906, 294, 264, 4001, 1002, 13, 51401], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 87, "seek": 32724, "start": 347.96000000000004, "end": 354.64, "text": " In IOS, a concept emerges directly from the resonant shape of a physical sensory input.", "tokens": [51401, 682, 286, 4367, 11, 257, 3410, 38965, 3838, 490, 264, 12544, 394, 3909, 295, 257, 4001, 27233, 4846, 13, 51735], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07675167979026327, "compression_ratio": 1.6181818181818182, "no_speech_prob": 3.216347327361646e-12}, {"id": 88, "seek": 35464, "start": 354.64, "end": 360.52, "text": " This physical approach exposes a glaring weakness in AI voice cloning and deepfakes.", "tokens": [50365, 639, 4001, 3109, 1278, 4201, 257, 1563, 1921, 12772, 294, 7318, 3177, 596, 16638, 293, 2452, 69, 3419, 13, 50659], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.052797621991260944, "compression_ratio": 1.5367965367965368, "no_speech_prob": 2.740093959022194e-12}, {"id": 89, "seek": 35464, "start": 360.52, "end": 366.65999999999997, "text": " When you analyze a synthetic audio file at the microsecond level, it lacks the complex, continuous", "tokens": [50659, 1133, 291, 12477, 257, 23420, 6278, 3991, 412, 264, 3123, 37841, 18882, 1496, 11, 309, 31132, 264, 3997, 11, 10957, 50966], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.052797621991260944, "compression_ratio": 1.5367965367965368, "no_speech_prob": 2.740093959022194e-12}, {"id": 90, "seek": 35464, "start": 366.65999999999997, "end": 370.24, "text": " emotional timing of a biological speaker.", "tokens": [50966, 6863, 10822, 295, 257, 13910, 8145, 13, 51145], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.052797621991260944, "compression_ratio": 1.5367965367965368, "no_speech_prob": 2.740093959022194e-12}, {"id": 91, "seek": 35464, "start": 370.24, "end": 375.46, "text": " Because the marine algorithm filters for that exact microtiming, it naturally extracts what", "tokens": [51145, 1436, 264, 20246, 9284, 15995, 337, 300, 1900, 3123, 10536, 332, 278, 11, 309, 8195, 8947, 82, 437, 51406], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.052797621991260944, "compression_ratio": 1.5367965367965368, "no_speech_prob": 2.740093959022194e-12}, {"id": 92, "seek": 35464, "start": 375.46, "end": 378.52, "text": " the developers call a soul signature.", "tokens": [51406, 264, 8849, 818, 257, 5133, 13397, 13, 51559], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.052797621991260944, "compression_ratio": 1.5367965367965368, "no_speech_prob": 2.740093959022194e-12}, {"id": 93, "seek": 37852, "start": 378.52, "end": 383.76, "text": " This is a cryptographic fingerprint generated by the specific biological jitter and harmonic", "tokens": [50365, 639, 307, 257, 9844, 12295, 30715, 10833, 538, 264, 2685, 13910, 361, 3904, 293, 32270, 50627], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 94, "seek": 37852, "start": 383.76, "end": 386.59999999999997, "text": " resonance of a real human voice.", "tokens": [50627, 30944, 295, 257, 957, 1952, 3177, 13, 50769], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 95, "seek": 37852, "start": 386.59999999999997, "end": 390.7, "text": " The system uses that wave pattern as the actual access gate.", "tokens": [50769, 440, 1185, 4960, 300, 5772, 5102, 382, 264, 3539, 2105, 8539, 13, 50974], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 96, "seek": 37852, "start": 390.7, "end": 396.58, "text": " If a fake audio file tries to interact with the grid, its flat, calculated timing will destructively", "tokens": [50974, 759, 257, 7592, 6278, 3991, 9898, 281, 4648, 365, 264, 10748, 11, 1080, 4962, 11, 15598, 10822, 486, 2677, 1757, 3413, 51268], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 97, "seek": 37852, "start": 396.58, "end": 398.84, "text": " interfere with the stored wave.", "tokens": [51268, 23946, 365, 264, 12187, 5772, 13, 51381], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 98, "seek": 37852, "start": 398.84, "end": 403.41999999999996, "text": " It simply fails to resonate, exposing its inauthenticity immediately.", "tokens": [51381, 467, 2935, 18199, 281, 34285, 11, 33178, 1080, 294, 40198, 317, 44198, 4258, 13, 51610], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05715843800748332, "compression_ratio": 1.6008230452674896, "no_speech_prob": 3.166130769019504e-12}, {"id": 99, "seek": 40342, "start": 403.42, "end": 408.6, "text": " The current leaders in artificial intelligence are building massive data factories, relying", "tokens": [50365, 440, 2190, 3523, 294, 11677, 7599, 366, 2390, 5994, 1412, 24813, 11, 24140, 50624], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08065453971304544, "compression_ratio": 1.6030534351145038, "no_speech_prob": 2.7293887636115066e-12}, {"id": 100, "seek": 40342, "start": 408.6, "end": 413.8, "text": " on static coordinates and brute force statistics to mimic human language.", "tokens": [50624, 322, 13437, 21056, 293, 47909, 3464, 12523, 281, 31075, 1952, 2856, 13, 50884], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08065453971304544, "compression_ratio": 1.6030534351145038, "no_speech_prob": 2.7293887636115066e-12}, {"id": 101, "seek": 40342, "start": 413.8, "end": 419.22, "text": " The MIM-8 architecture suggests that real intelligence requires physical boundaries.", "tokens": [50884, 440, 376, 6324, 12, 23, 9482, 13409, 300, 957, 7599, 7029, 4001, 13180, 13, 51155], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08065453971304544, "compression_ratio": 1.6030534351145038, "no_speech_prob": 2.7293887636115066e-12}, {"id": 102, "seek": 40342, "start": 419.22, "end": 424.64, "text": " It needs a system that experiences the passage of time, requires offline sleep to maintain its", "tokens": [51155, 467, 2203, 257, 1185, 300, 5235, 264, 11497, 295, 565, 11, 7029, 21857, 2817, 281, 6909, 1080, 51426], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08065453971304544, "compression_ratio": 1.6030534351145038, "no_speech_prob": 2.7293887636115066e-12}, {"id": 103, "seek": 40342, "start": 424.64, "end": 430.04, "text": " health, and interprets the world through a filter of emotional importance.", "tokens": [51426, 1585, 11, 293, 17489, 1373, 264, 1002, 807, 257, 6608, 295, 6863, 7379, 13, 51696], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08065453971304544, "compression_ratio": 1.6030534351145038, "no_speech_prob": 2.7293887636115066e-12}, {"id": 104, "seek": 43004, "start": 430.04, "end": 434.72, "text": " Physical intelligence might not emerge from adding more processors to a giant calculator.", "tokens": [50365, 31918, 7599, 1062, 406, 21511, 490, 5127, 544, 27751, 281, 257, 7410, 24993, 13, 50599], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2102375030517578, "compression_ratio": 1.3835616438356164, "no_speech_prob": 2.8487793721221344e-12}, {"id": 105, "seek": 43004, "start": 434.72, "end": 440.28000000000003, "text": " Rather, it may require engineering a living substrate that actually knows how to resonate with", "tokens": [50599, 16571, 11, 309, 815, 3651, 7043, 257, 2647, 27585, 300, 767, 3255, 577, 281, 34285, 365, 50877], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2102375030517578, "compression_ratio": 1.3835616438356164, "no_speech_prob": 2.8487793721221344e-12}, {"id": 106, "seek": 43004, "start": 440.28000000000003, "end": 441.28000000000003, "text": " a physical world.", "tokens": [50877, 257, 4001, 1002, 13, 50927], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2102375030517578, "compression_ratio": 1.3835616438356164, "no_speech_prob": 2.8487793721221344e-12}], "language": "en"}